The,isoHunt,website,provides,an,advanced,BitTorrent,search,engine,that,searches,over,million,files,from,a,single,location,It,also,provides,cross,referenced,statistics,for,all,torrents,indexed,and,updated,to,the,hour,isoHunt,provides,a,RESTful,JSON,API,so,that,developers,may,access,its,search,capabilities,programmatically,This,API,is,freely,available,on,the,condition,that,if,the,resulting,app,is,publicly,available,to,users,developers,must,link,to,torrent,details,pages,on,isoHunt,com,regardless,of,whether,or,not,they,link,to,the,torrent,files,themselves